{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-081","title":"消费心理","sectionId":"chapter-04","sectionTitle":"商店购物买买买","pageStart":416,"pageEnd":420,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":13,"duplicateEntryCount":21,"pages":[{"number":416,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"81 消费心理"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"consumer psychology 消费心理","headword":"consumer psychology"},{"type":"entry","text":"client service 客户服务","headword":"client service"},{"type":"entry","text":"purchasing power 购买力","headword":"purchasing power"},{"type":"entry","text":"high income 高收入","headword":"high income"}]},{"number":417,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"best sellers 畅销品","headword":"best sellers"},{"type":"entry","text":"supply and demand 供应与需求","headword":"supply and demand"},{"type":"entry","text":"target audience 目标客户","headword":"target audience"},{"type":"entry","text":"customer demand 客户需求","headword":"customer demand"}]},{"number":418,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"propensity to consume 消费倾向","headword":"propensity to consume"},{"type":"entry","text":"realistic psychology 求实心理","headword":"realistic psychology"},{"type":"entry","text":"cheap and fine 物美价廉","headword":"cheap and fine"},{"type":"entry","text":"take advantage of 占…便宜","headword":"take advantage of"}]},{"number":419,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"silly idea愚蠢的想法","headword":"silly idea"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"text","text":"有趣的小词wise"},{"type":"text","text":"1. Hey! Wise up! 放聪明点好吗？"},{"type":"text","text":"当别人做了什么傻事时，你可以说Don’t be stupid.或是Don’t be"},{"type":"text","text":"silly. 但是这两种说法显得不是很礼貌。比较客气一点的说法是Wise"},{"type":"text","text":"up!老外有时还会说Hey! Grow up! 意思就是“你成熟一点好不好？”例"},{"type":"text","text":"如，你有一个朋友做事很没有主见，你们一起逛街，发现一件裙子很"},{"type":"text","text":"漂亮，你鼓动她买下，可她却说要回家征求父母的意见，你就可以说"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey! Grow up!"},{"type":"text","text":"2. Don’t look wise.别自作聪明。"}]},{"number":420,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"有些人总喜欢自以为是、自作聪明，碰到这种人你肯定很厌烦，"},{"type":"text","text":"这时候你就可以毫不客气地对他（她）说Don’t look wise。"}]}]}